com.calendarfx.view

Class CalendarView

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Styleable, EventTarget, Skinnable

    public class CalendarView
extends DateControl
    A full calendar view with multiple pages for displaying a single day, a week, a month, and an entire year. The view also includes two trays, one for seeing all calendar sources, and one for seeing the results of the current search. The trays can be shown or hidden. Another nice feature is direct support for printing (see getPrintView()).
